web-driver-spike
================
This project has been created as ruby + web-driver spike

Author: Kamil Marek

CONFIGURATION
========================
1/ install ruby 
2/ gem install selenium-webdriver
3/ configure credentials in lib/TestCase.rb

HOW TO USE IT:
==============
1/ to run tests
ruby run_tests.rb

2/ to add new test cases
- create new file in test_cases directory
- add test to test suite in run_tests.rb

Naming convention for test cases: 
- SomeTestCase for class and file name
- some_test_case for test case name stored in test suite, 
it will be automatically converted into SomeTestCase format